00:17:16.060 --> 00:17:18.580
from his point of
view, Hunter, right.

00:17:18.580 --> 00:17:23.190
And then two other girls, they
live with their paternal aunts,

00:17:23.190 --> 00:17:26.650
one in Phoenix, one in
