00:18:07.070 --> 00:18:08.850
She's had a job for a while.

00:18:08.850 --> 00:18:10.150
He's three.

00:18:10.150 --> 00:18:13.110
So she's had the same job
for a couple years and she's,

00:18:13.110 --> 00:18:15.860
