that they didn't have
your book "Tricks."

00:20:36.040 --> 00:20:39.460
So I contacted them about
it because it's odd.

00:20:39.460 --> 00:20:41.170
They had all of your
other books.

00:20:41.170 --> 00:20:43.970
And it appears that
it's being challenged.

00:20:43.970 --> 00:20:48.520
